OL,3,CMan and women killed in Glenariffe van
OL,4,Ccrash
OL,6,FTwo people have died following a road
OL,7,Fcollision in Co Antrim.
OL,9,FA 41-year-old man and a 31-year-old
OL,10,Fwoman died following the incident
OL,11,Finvolving a van in the Glenariffe area
OL,12,Fof Ballymena on Saturday.
OL,14,FA police spokesperson said they
OL,15,Freceived a report of the crash
OL,16,Finvolving a silver Ford Transit Custom
OL,17,Fvan in the Glenariffe Road area
OL,18,Fshortly before 9.10pm.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
