OL,3,CMan and women killed in Glenariffe van
OL,4,Ccrash
OL,6,F"Officers, along with colleagues from
OL,7,Fthe Northern Ireland Ambulance
OL,8,FService, and Northern Ireland Fire and
OL,9,FRescue Service attended," they said.
OL,11,F"The occupants of the van, a 41-year-
OL,12,Fold man, and 31-year-old woman, were
OL,13,Fboth sadly pronounced deceased at the
OL,14,Fscene.
OL,16,F"No other injuries were reported. The
OL,17,FGlenariffe Road, which was closed for
OL,18,Fa time, has since fully reopened.
